「'''霍夫蟹'''」（{{lang|en|"'''Hoff crab'''"}}；''Kiwa n. sp.''）是[[十足目|十足目]][[異尾下目|異尾下目]][[劣柱蝦總科|劣柱蝦總科]][[基瓦科|基瓦科]]的[[未命名物種|未命名物種]]，是除了[[基瓦多毛怪|基瓦多毛怪]]及[[雪人蟹|雪人蟹]]以外的第三個物種。本物種於2010年在[[南極|南極]]附近[[斯科舍板块|斯科舍板块]]上[[東斯科舍洋脊|東斯科舍洋脊]]的[[海底熱泉|海底熱泉]]發現<ref name="thurber">{{cite journal |author=Andrew R. Thurber, William J. Jones & Kareen Schnabel |year=2011 |title=Dancing for food in the deep sea: bacterial farming by a new species of yeti crab |journal=[[PLoS_ONE|PLoS ONE]] |volume=6 |issue=11 |page=e26243 |doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0026243|url=http://www.plosone.org/article/info%3Adoi%2F10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0026243}}</ref><ref name="Rogers 2012">{{cite journal |author=Alex D. Rogers, Paul A. Tyler, Douglas P. Connelly, Jon T. Copley, Rachael James, Robert D. Larter, Katrin Linse, Rachel A. Mills, Alfredo Naveira Garabato, Richard D. Pancost, David A. Pearce, Nicholas V. C. Polunin, Christopher R. German, Timothy Shank, Philipp H. Boersch-Supan, Belinda J. Alker, Alfred Aquilina, Sarah A. Bennett, Andrew Clarke, Robert J. J. Dinley, Alastair G. C. Graham, Darryl R. H. Green, Jeffrey A. Hawkes, Laura Hepburn, Ana Hilario, Veerle A. I. Huvenne, Leigh Marsh, Eva Ramirez-Llodra, William D. K. Reid, Christopher N. Roterman, Christopher J. Sweeting, Sven Thatje & Katrin Zwirglmaier |year=2012 |title=The discovery of new deep-sea hydrothermal vent communities in the Southern Ocean and implications for biogeography |journal=[[PLoS_Biology|PLoS Biology]] |volume=10 |issue=1 |page=e1001234 |doi=10.1371/journal.pbio.1001234 |ref=Rogers2012 |pmid=22235194}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=ChEsSo – Exploration for vents south of the Polar Front |url=http://www.noc.soton.ac.uk/chess/science/chesso.html |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527190145/http://www.noc.soton.ac.uk/chess/science/chesso.html |archivedate=2012-05-27 }}</ref> ，其後又於2011年在[[西南印度洋脊|西南印度洋脊]]的[[深海噴泉|深海噴泉]]再次發現<ref name=bbc>{{cite news |title=Deep-sea creatures at volcanic vent |author=Rebecca Morelle |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |language=en |date=2011-12-28 |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-16267625}}</ref>。

這一種「霍夫蟹」於2010年得名於[[美國演員|美國演員]][[大衛·赫索霍夫|大衛·赫索霍夫]]<ref>{{cite news |title='The Hoff' crab is new ocean find|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-16394430 |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=4 January 2012}}</ref>，現時根據其[[线粒体DNA|线粒体DNA]]及[[細胞核|細胞核]]的[[rDNA|rDNA]]分析，確認這物種在遺傳學上與基瓦多毛怪是不同的物種兩者大約在1200萬年前分開<ref name="Rogers 2012" />。

